data.description: Home comes with a home warranty! This stunning home offers comfort, style & spaciousness. W/ over 2200 sqft of well-designed space, this 4 bdrm, 2 bath home is a true gem. Step inside where you'll immediately notice the beautiful tile floors throughout; elegant & easy to maintain. The open-concept floor plan seamlessly connects the living room, dining & kitchen, creating a welcoming atmosphere for both family gatherings & entertaining friends. The kitchen offers functionality & style boasting granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. The master suite is a true sanctuary, w/ double vanity, soaking tub, separate shower & walk-in closet. One of the highlights is the backyard oasis w/ screened lanai & sparkling salt water pool, perfect for cooling off on hot Florida days. Beyond the pool are breathtaking views of the serene pond, creating a peaceful backdrop for outdoor activities & relaxation. Here, you're buying more than a home, you're buying a lifestyle... golf cart parades, ladies nights & monthly cornhole, to the clubhouse, pool, fitness center, tennis & more. Don't miss your chance to surround yourself with amazing neighbors in the SPECTACULAR COMMUNITY of Portico!
